Invocation Name: jon skeet facts
des:
We all love Jon Skeet. He has spent so much of his time helping other programmers that its priceless. He has answered so many question on Stack Overflow, thus setting the highest standard one can achieve. This is a tribute to all the facts about him that came as a reply, when someone asked : "Who is Jon Skeet".
Thank You Sir. We love and respect you very much from the core of our heart. This is just a humble skill to pay my respect.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
